Description_lang: Release all healing stored in The Well of Existence into an ally. This healing is amplified by $?a296200[$296200s1][$s2]%.$?a296201[ The Well will not release more healing than needed to fully heal the target.][]

description_blz.en_US: Release all healing stored in The Well of Existence into an ally. This healing is amplified by 20%.
description_blz.es_MX: Libera la sanación almacenada dentro del Pozo de la existencia hacia un aliado. Esta sanación se amplifica un 20%.
description_blz.pt_BR: Libera em um aliado toda a cura armazenada no Poço da Existência. Essa cura é aumentada em 20%.
description_blz.de_DE: Gibt sämtliche im Quell des Seins gespeicherte Heilung an einen Verbündeten ab. Diese Heilung wird um 20% verstärkt.
description_blz.en_GB: Release all healing stored in The Well of Existence into an ally. This healing is amplified by 20%.
description_blz.es_ES: Libera toda la sanación almacenada en el pozo de la existencia sobre un aliado. Esta sanación se amplifica un 20%.
description_blz.fr_FR: Libère tous les points de soins stockés dans le puits d’existence pour un allié. Ces soins sont amplifiés de 20%.
description_blz.it_IT: Rilascia tutte le cure immagazzinate nel Pozzo dell'Esistenza su un alleato. Queste cure sono amplificate del 20%.
description_blz.ru_RU: Передает сохраненное в Источнике бытия здоровье союзнику. Это исцеление усиливается на 20%.
description_blz.ko_KR: 존재의 샘에 저장된 모든 치유량을 아군에게 방출합니다. 이 치유량은 20%만큼 증폭됩니다.]
description_blz.zh_TW: 將儲存在萬物之井中的所有治療量向一位盟友釋放。治療量會增幅20%。
description_blz.zh_CN: 将储存在存续之井中的所有治疗量注入一位盟友体内。这次治疗的治疗效果将获得20%的增强。
